OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777140665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 17-year-old
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Chesterfield
OL,6,FThe family of a 17-year-old girl, who
OL,7,Fdied in a crash near Chesterfield,
OL,8,Fhave said her death has left a
OL,9,F'cataclysmic hole' in their life.
OL,11,FSummer was a passenger in a Vauxhall
OL,12,FCorsa which left the road and was in
OL,13,Fcollision with a tree in Sutton Lane,
OL,14,FSutton Scarsdale on Sunday 19 April.
OL,16,FThe 17-year-old suffered serious
OL,17,Finjuries and lost her life at the
OL,18,Fscene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
