FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777140665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 17-year-old
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Chesterfield
OL,6,FThree other passengers in the car were
OL,7,Finjured, two seriously and one less
OL,8,Fbadly.
OL,10,FThe 19-year-old driver had minor
OL,11,Finjuries and was arrested on suspicion
OL,12,Fof causing death by dangerous driving
OL,13,Fand causing serious injury by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving.
OL,16,FSummer's mum has now paid tribute to
OL,17,Fher, saying: "Summer was an outgoing
OL,18,Fyoung girl, full of life, bubbly, very
OL,19,Fchatty and loved being the centre of
OL,20,Fattention.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777140665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 17-year-old
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Chesterfield
OL,6,F"She was very motivated and knew where
OL,7,Fshe wanted to go in life.
OL,9,F"She was very family orientated and
OL,10,Fadored her little sisters Bonnie and
OL,11,FBella.
OL,13,F"Summer was an incredibly loved
OL,14,Fdaughter, sister, niece and cousin.
OL,16,F"She was just enjoying living life to
OL,17,Fthe fullest as a 17-year-old."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
