OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 17-year-old
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Chesterfield
OL,6,FSummer's dad added: "Growing up Summer
OL,7,Floved baking and cooking, making
OL,8,FYoutube videos, going to watch
OL,9,FMansfield Town, helping out with
OL,10,Fhousehold tasks and being mischievous.
OL,12,F"She loved telling random jokes to her
OL,13,Fgranddad George and dad Rob. Her
OL,14,Fgrandad doted on Summer, giving her
OL,15,Fthe name Twinkle, due to her lighting
OL,16,Fup his day when he spent time with
OL,17,Fher. He would always struggle to say
OL,18,Fno to her if she needed anything.
OL,20,F"We are very proud to have Summer as
OL,21,Four daughter and granddaughter.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
