OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777140665
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 17-year-old
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Chesterfield
OL,6,F"She was always smiling and lit up
OL,7,Fevery room she entered with her
OL,8,Ftwinkly, chatty personality.
OL,10,F"Summer's death has left a cataclysmic
OL,11,Fhole in her whole family's life and
OL,12,Feveryone who knew Summer."
